extends ../templates/base.pug
include ../templates/mixins.pug

block preheader
  | As requested, we've updated your password. If you made this change, you don't need to do anything else.

block content
  h1 Hi #{user.firstName}
  p The password for your !{config.get('company.name')} account has been updated. If you made this change, you don't need to do anything else.
  p
    | If you did not recently update your password and believe an unauthorized person has accessed your account, please
    |
    a(href=`mailto:${config.get('company.supportEmail')}`) contact support
    | .
  p
    | Thanks,
    br
    | The !{config.get('company.name')} Team
